content.html: After watching Ep.3 of Andor, I was like "This is probably the best SW series I watched so far". Now I'm at Ep.8, and I'm like "This is the best TV-Show I've watched in the last 5 years". Star Wars Andor is a masterpiece.
content.value:
After watching Ep.3 of Andor, I was like "This is probably the best SW series I watched so far".
